dataObjects.title: Astrodoras asterifrons
dataObjects.bibliographicCitation: "Astrodoras asterifrons." Wikipedia, The Free Encyclopedia. 17 Mar 2013, 01:35 UTC. 3 Mar 2014 <http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Astrodoras_asterifrons&oldid=597673391>.
dataObjects.description:
Astrodoras asterifrons is the only species in the genus Astrodoras of the catfish (order Siluriformes) family Doradidae.[1] This species originates from the Amazon basin of Bolivia and Brazil and reaches a length of about 8.0 centimetres (3.1 in) SL.[2] This genus is the type genus of the subfamily Astrodoradinae.[3]
